sign by Finbarr Sheehy")) (media:content ((height . "304") (lang . " ") (type . "image/png") (width . "460") (url . "http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2013/4/10/1365599093205/Thatcher_Funeral2.png")) (media:credit ((scheme . "urn:ebu")) "Guardian") (media:description nil "Click to view the interactive guide to Margaret Thatcher's funeral")))) ("Information is Beautiful: who can catch which flu?" "<div class=\"track\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hits.guardian.co.uk/b/ss/guardiangu-feeds/1/H.25.4/14330?ns=guardian&pageName=Data%3Ainformation-beautiful-who-can-catch-which-flu%3A1891805&ch=News&c3=GU.co.uk&c4=UK+news%2CHealth+%28Society%29%2CFlu+%28Society%29%2CChina+%28News%29%2CData+visualisation+%28Technology+-+add+to+pieces+about+not+examples+of%29%2CBird+flu+%28News%29%2CSwine+flu&c5=Unclassified%2CNot+commercially+useful%2CHealth+Society%2CHealth&c6=David+McCandless&c7=2013%2F04%2F10+12%3A53&c8=1891805&c9=Blog&c10=Blogpost&c13=Show+and+Tell+%28dataviz+series%29&c19=GUK&c25=Datablog&c47=UK&c64=UK&c65=Information+is+Beautiful%3A+who+can+catch+which+flu%3F&c66=News&c72=&c73=&c74=&c75=&h2=GU%2FNews%2FNews%2FHealth\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /></div><p class=\"standfirst\">A new strain of bird flu has broken out in the Shanghai area of Eastern China. <strong>David McCandless</strong> asks who can catch which flu?<br />• <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/data\">More data journalism and data visualisations from the Guardian</a></p><p>H7N9? H5N1? H1N1? H9N2? H7N7? </p><p>A new, deadly strain of \"bird flu\" - H7N9- has <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/apr/06/bird-flu-threat-shanghai-markets\">broken out in the Shanghai area of Eastern China</a>.</p><p>Is this strain worse than H5N1? Or H1N1? Or even H2N2? We weren't sure. So we took a look at the data and... well, you can guess the rest. Click on the image above to view the full-size graphic.</p><h2><br /><strong>The data</strong></h2><p>Complete list of all flu types, sources and ex