ltax\">Council tax</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"author\"><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/profile/patrickbutler\">Patrick Butler</a></div><br/><div class=\"terms\"><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk\">guardian.co.uk</a> &copy; 2013 Guardian News and Media Limited or its affiliated companies. All rights reserved. | Use of this content is subject to our <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/help/terms-of-service\">Terms & Conditions</a> | <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/help/feeds\">More Feeds</a></div><p style=\"clear:both\" /><img width='1' height='1' src='http://guardian.co.uk.feedsportal.com/c/34708/f/643782/s/2a341fe6/mf.gif' border='0'/><div class='mf-viral'><table border='0'><tr><td valign='middle'><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/viral/sendEmail.cfm?lang=en&title=Every+welfare+cut+listed%3A+how+much+a+typical+family+will+lose+per+week&link=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.guardian.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fdatablog%2F2013%2Fapr%2F01%2Fevery-welfare-cut-listed\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td></tr></table></div><br/><br/><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/161990837969/u/49/f/643782/c/34708/s/2a341fe6/kg/355/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/161990837969/u/49/f/643782/c/34708/s/2a341fe6/kg/355/a2.img\" border=\"0\"/></a><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/161990837969/u/49/f/643782/c/34708/s/2a341fe6/kg/355/a2t.img\" border=\"0\"/>" "http://www.guardian.co.uk/news/datablog/2013/apr/01/every-welfare-cut-listed" (20824 49196) old 20 nil nil ((title nil "Every welfare cut listed: how much a typical family will lose per week") (link nil "http://www.guardian.co.uk/news/datablog/2013/apr/01/every-welfare-cut-listed") (description nil "<div class=\"track\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hits.guardian.co.uk/b/ss/guardiangu-feeds/1/H.25.4/33244?ns=guardian&pageName=Data%3Aevery-welfare-cut-listed%3A1886904&ch=News&c3=GU.co.uk&c4=UK+news%2CWelfare+%28Politics%29%2CSociet